## What I implemented (code complete, unverified)

**S7-5 — attach 连线同步**
- New pure module `src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/canvas/effectEdgeSync.ts`: effect-edge model (`data.edgeKind:"effect"`, `effectKind:"attach"|"unmount"`), distinguishable styles (attach=green dashed「挂载」, unmount=orange dashed「卸载」), `reconcileEffectEdgesForCard` (forward, idempotent), `collectRemovedEffectRefs`/`applyEffectRemovalsToNodes`/`removeEffectRowFromCard` (reverse-delete), `appendMountEffectRow` (reverse drag-create).
- New `com/effects/mount/MountEffectPanel.tsx` + `MountTargetModal.tsx` (modal target picker; role defaults to target card owner; dropdowns only, no free-text id).
- Forward sync in `applyNodeData` (rebuild edges on apply); reverse in `useStoryCanvasGraph.onEdgesChange` (delete edge → drop row) and `canvasConnectHandlers` (modifier-drag from exit → append attach row + edge); `onConnectStart` wired into the stage.
- Seeded a mock attach effect edge (`card_intro`→`card_boss`) for visual distinction.

**S7-6 — unmount + summary + 收口**
- `unmount_call_card` reuses the same mount panel/edge mechanism (blank = current card/agent).
- New `summarizeEffect(effect, params, sources?)` bis helper; `ExitEffectsMockList` auto-derives summary and stops overwriting once the user edits it (dirty-aware).
- Wired both attach/unmount into `ExitEffectPanel` dispatch (all 14 effects now have dedicated panels).
- Tests: `tests/storyEditor/effectEdgeSync.test.ts`, `tests/storyEditor/summarizeEffect.test.ts`.
- Docs: added §5.4/§5.5 + §6.3 note to `02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿.md`.

